						               													<description>Disposable Heroes 2 is a WWII platoon level historical miniature wargaming system. It is designed not just to put you in command of the troops and weapons of a WWII platoon but in the historical tactical situation of a platoon commander. It is your rifle squads that will carry your attack forward, or be the difference between holding the line or the enemy breaking through. Disposable Heroes 2 recreates a realistic tactical battlefield situation of a platoon commander.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Disposable Heroes 2 features:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Realistic ground scale and platoon frontage&amp;#10;Effective Fog of War system.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Accurate availability &amp;amp; deployment of platoons&amp;#10;Singular command and control system.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is not just another platoon-level WWII system. Disposable Heroes 2 offers a unique tactical challenge with a focus on recreating the actual battlefield conditions that platoons fought in.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
